Digital Dice with 7-Segment Display

ğŸ”¹ About the Project:

 This project replaces traditional dice with a digital, tamper-proof 
version using an Arduino, a button, and a seven-segment display. Each 
button press generates a fair random number from 1 to 6.

ğŸ”¹ Features:
True randomness using Arduino's random function


Instant number display on seven-segment


Compact, reliable, and easy to use


ğŸ”¹ Why it's Awesome:
No cheating possible


Never lose your dice again


Great for board games, math learning, and fun activities!


